{"tid":195893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這名男子挑戰「連續30天每天喝3公斤水」","createTime":"2017-04-11T02:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T02:44:47.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81f1389239c9f46f5f8ef46a5cf70ec7d917bd83","tid":195893,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:29:08.000Z","msg":"我們都知道多喝水對身體健康有好處，國外的一位網友就決定要挑戰「連續30天每天喝一加侖（約3.78公斤）水」，想要看看每天攝入足夠多的水會對身體帶來什麼改變。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160410/1460274009214108.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20160410%2F1460274009214108.jpg&h=cfc2dac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第1天：<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160410/1460274020432850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20160410%2F1460274020432850.jpg&h=081e6a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於要喝的水太多了，他乾脆直接走哪都帶著裝水的大瓶子，結果當晚到11:30次才完成任務。<br />\n<br />\n第5天：<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160410/1460274029795284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20160410%2F1460274029795284.jpg&h=baa97d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他感覺整天都在喝水，而且吃的少了，因為肚子總是飽的，而且他每過20分鐘就要上一次廁所，辦公室的同事差點以為他是因為嗑藥導致身體出了問題。<br />\n<br />\n第10天：<br />\n他注意到自己的身體開始發生變化，他感覺自己好像變帥了一點。以前早晨他需要一杯咖啡才能夠讓自己清醒開工，但是現在早上醒來就感覺神清氣爽。<br />\n他依然是每天到哪裡都帶著大水瓶，就算是在床上也不例外，每天用手臂拿水瓶，他感覺臂力有增強了，不過每天要喝完一加侖的水依然是一件很有難度的事情。<br />\n<br />\n第15天：<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160410/1460274043231727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20160410%2F1460274043231727.jpg&h=f02d1d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他明顯感覺自己變得精力充沛，他以往每天都至少要喝兩杯咖啡提神，但是現在幾乎不喝咖啡了。傍晚跑步的時候，也覺得速度更快了，晚上的睡眠質量也提高了。他以往的時候晚上睡覺總感覺燥熱，現在沒有這種感覺了。<br />\n而且沒有喝水的時候他經常都會感覺很渴，好像他的身體已經適應了這種攝入這麼多水量的生活方式，他感覺自己可能回不到以前那樣了。<br />\n<br />\n第20天：<br />\n身邊的人說感覺他現在更快樂一些了~<br />\n<br />\n第25天：<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160410/1460274055937277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20160410%2F1460274055937277.jpg&h=12d67639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n還是每天頻繁上廁所，但是他的朋友說他的膚質變好了，而且他感覺非常有活力，自我感覺非常好。他已經不覺得喝下一加侖的水是一個難題或者挑戰了，已經完全適應了這種狀態。<br />\n<br />\n第30天：<br />\n挑戰的最後一天還是上很多遍廁所，而且一直感覺很渴，他覺得每天喝一加侖的水有些過量，但是他還是感覺沒有喝夠水。<br />\n他並不建議每個人都喝這麼多的水，因為這樣可能會讓你的胃部受到傷害。如果是在戶外做體力工作，那就需要比在室內進行腦力工作攝入更多的水。<br />\n這樣的結果是不是也讓你覺得很驚艷呢？其實健康人有很強的調節和適應能力，水喝多了能排出去，水喝少了身體會發出口渴的信號促使你去喝水，因此不必對於飲水量有太多擔心，但是工作忙的時候也要記得喝水哦~分享出去，讓大家看到這個有趣的挑戰吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fullyu.com/article/6459/%E5%96%9D%E6%B0%B4%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Farticle%2F6459%2F%25E5%2596%259D%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%258C%2591%25E6%2588%25B0%2F&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=24416c35\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fullyu.com/article/6459/%E5%96%9D%E6%B0%B4%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"272def8a557a8ff3e4dafdfa0c8bffa7188d3558","tid":195893,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:30:37.000Z","msg":"Content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cde7f5478718958c5e163465a1a2e2385c7320","tid":195893,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n?"},{"pid":"d08691a729bbebc7ffe5c0ec647c4aa156758e56","tid":195893,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n?</blockquote><br />\ngoogle下啦豬兜"},{"pid":"edb95d1dbc8614e0a034c046f93a3c67d6fd6855","tid":195893,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:39:15.000Z","msg":"content farm 垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鳩up一大輪<br />\n最後結論又係: 無結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da00f45f81def401a9c7c5186ceb5328354655c8","tid":195893,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"手淫的力量.jpg"},{"pid":"cfc88e26a7c4c7af98638063c4676e60b22c25a9","tid":195893,"uid":27509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"我有一排一日飲5公升水<br />\n結論係15分鐘要去一次廁所好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8bfdb9eeb8191a7ff39903f35af6a758f44157","tid":195893,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手淫的力量.jpg</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/104324_ca42d5fdfc5caf1d0faa618c6adb2188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F104324_ca42d5fdfc5caf1d0faa618c6adb2188.jpg&h=7c605b81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00c07d797d98d90a68cfeae28758f38200dd576e","tid":195893,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n?</blockquote><br />\ngoogle下啦豬兜</blockquote><br />\n可能人地係&quot;作者&quot;"},{"pid":"54210d3d84efacdac5f433212e8c556bb7b304cd","tid":195893,"uid":15558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>手淫的力量.jpg</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/104324_ca42d5fdfc5caf1d0faa618c6adb2188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F104324_ca42d5fdfc5caf1d0faa618c6adb2188.jpg&h=7c605b81&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n無論翻睇左幾多次呢個reverse版同original版都係咁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}